## Description {#details}

Iterator for locations and the values they contain.

Dereferencing produces a struct/pair containing the <a href="/docs/api/classes/livedebugvalues/locidx">LocIdx</a> key for this location, and a reference to the value currently stored. Simplifies the process of seeking a particular location.
